scenes.description: Hakos Baelz talks about her new song 'FEAST' and upcoming content.
Announcement regarding streaming services for her new music.
Baelz checks in with the audience and reflects on the live performance.
Baelz discusses her focus on dance and expresses hope that her effort was visible.
Closing remarks, thanking fans for 'Baebry', and final goodbyes.
Ending credits featuring behind-the-scenes dance practice footage and staff credits.
